    covered by this License.
  "Licensor" — LEE Inhee (이인희) / Parandurume Inc. (파란두루미).
  "Contributors" — Anyone who has added code, documentation, or other materials
    to the Software. This includes generative AI systems used in development.
  "User" — Any person or organization exercising rights under this License.
